Age group segmentation is another key aspect in the ecotourism market as travelers of different age groups have varying preferences and expectations. By targeting millennials, families, senior citizens, and other specific age groups, businesses can design experiences and packages that resonate with the unique interests and capabilities of each segment, thereby enhancing customer satisfaction and loyalty.

